OL,3,CVital funds raised for charity
OL,4,Cproviding lifesaving care
OL,6,FA campaigner from Lancashire has
OL,7,Fhosted a special charity football
OL,8,Fmatch to support the North West
OL,9,FAmbulance Service.
OL,11,FZack Kerr, 30, who has cerebral palsy
OL,12,Fand uses an electric wheelchair,
OL,13,Forganised the big day in Accrington to
OL,14,Fraise vital funds for the charity.
OL,16,FThe cause is close to his heart after
OL,17,Fparamedics helped save his mum's life
OL,18,Fwhen she suffered a shock heart attack
OL,19,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
