OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777903634
OL,3,CVital funds raised for charity
OL,4,Cproviding lifesaving care
OL,6,FZack - who his best known for his
OL,7,Fsuccessful "Changing Places" campaign
OL,8,Fand was named a winner at the National
OL,9,FDiversity Awards - had hoped to raise
OL,10,F#10,000 for vital equipment and
OL,11,Fsupport services for the charity.
OL,13,FThe Honorary Freeman of Hyndburn has
OL,14,Fsurpassed that target - raising over
OL,15,F#17,000 - which the family are
OL,16,Fdelighted about.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
