PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777903634
OL,3,CVital funds raised for charity
OL,4,Cproviding lifesaving care
OL,6,FOff the pitch, the event included a
OL,7,Fmascot race, a community market with
OL,8,Fstalls and raffles and family
OL,9,Factivities throughout the day.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Katie Walderman on ITV
OL,12,FGranada Reports last month, Zack said
OL,13,Fthe ambulance crews were "unsung
OL,14,Fheroes" and and said his mum, Krissy,
OL,15,Fis now recovering well ` and even
OL,16,Fhelping him organise the event.
OL,18,FA football shirt auction is still
OL,19,Frunning which is expected to end next
OL,20,Fweekend.
